          <title>Fireworks mortars, fuel canisters found in Cybertruck that exploded outside Trump hotel in Las Vegas</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A Cybertruck explosion outside of the Trump International Hotel in Las Vegas was caused by firework mortars and camp fuel canisters, according to investigators. The explosion killed one person inside the vehicle and injured at least seven others nearby.]]></description>
